    "v05.tooltip.Rushbrooke_tautology": "Standard Rushbrooke hyperscaling 2β + γ_χ = ν·d at d=1. In TAF this is a TAUTOLOGY — γ_χ is defined exactly so this holds. Confirmed by Sage Groebner basis.",
